{"tid":2135594,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：Microsoft或將接管Tiktok美國業務","createTime":"2020-08-01T14:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T05:03:29.000Z","uid":318037,"like":8,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"8cbfd8d4ec5e73209b4c18ffa286634772ac9481","tid":2135594,"uid":318037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:00:56.000Z","msg":"兩名知情人士週六表示，在特朗普表示他已決定禁止TikTok後，字節跳動已同意完全剝離TikTok在美國的業務，以輓救與白宮的一筆交易。字節跳動此前曾試圖在TikTok的美國業務中持有少數股權，但遭到了白宮的拒絕。根據新的交易提議，字節跳動將完全退出，而微軟將接管TikTok在美業務。消息人士補充稱，一些總部位於美國的字節跳動投資者可能有機會獲得該業務的少數股權。美國白宮、字節跳動和微軟均未對此消息置評。"},{"pid":"c3df25fae27f38095402a2d21e3c2104084d7ccf","tid":2135594,"uid":32722,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"呢個平台旨在減低人類智商，係唔係中國係背後操控都應該被消滅"},{"pid":"bb447047bc4018c14f03d30f4b3e2bef9a56a61b","tid":2135594,"uid":120499,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"Ban 咗MSFT啦"},{"pid":"9304d68c1a7488de1551fc9f09d2e1a8004d4456","tid":2135594,"uid":198175,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"咁玩法, MS真係可以執到平貨<br />\n<br />\n如果最後一刻MS唔肯接手, 支那就要硬食total loss<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟手MS會去review apps D source code 同server routing, 到時就會發現支那D後台古惑嘢, 一係支那IT佬臨撤出時消滅晒D apps source code同剷咗個server<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba29ca4539f04bd97497012016c6e61876805a8","tid":2135594,"uid":21602,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"Facebook下個月都會推出instagram Reels<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同tictok差唔多既野<br />\n如果直接ban美國唔洗比錢中國<br />\n如果msft買就可能要面對fb挑戰"},{"pid":"b6d66bf7ce4d1909e374fd3bcc41f16c07cb4d6a","tid":2135594,"uid":273228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dba29ca4539f04bd97497012016c6e61876805a8","tid":2135594,"uid":21602,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"ci